{"body": "An applicant’s capital is to be treated as yielding—\na monthly income of £4.35 for each £250 in excess of £6,000 and £4.35 for any excess which is not a complete £250, or\na weekly income of £1 for each £250 in excess of £6,000 and £1 for any excess which is not a complete £250.\nParagraph (1) does not apply where the capital is disregarded or the actual income from that capital is taken into account under regulation 57(1)(j) (income from an annuity) or 57(1)(k) (income from a trust).\nWhere an applicant’s capital is treated as yielding income, any actual income derived from that capital, for example rental, interest or dividends, is to be treated as part of the applicant’s capital from the day it is due to be paid to the applicant.", "citation_label": "SSI 2021/249 reg. 63", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/ssi/2021/249/63", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "Regulation 63", "id": "76306621-e7af-5441-9d82-f96375b45dca", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "249", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "63", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "ssi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2021"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "SSI 2021/249 reg. 63", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["S"], "references_to": ["ssi/2021/249"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 63, "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_document_id": "ssi/2021/249", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/regulation/63", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital-r2026-07-20-datefix/ssi/2021/249/regulation-63.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/regulation/63", "version": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital-r2026-07-20-datefix"}
{"body": "No person is entitled to council tax reduction if that person’s capital exceeds £16,000.", "citation_label": "SSI 2021/249 reg. 66", "citation_path": "uk/regulation/ssi/2021/249/66", "document_class": "regulation", "expression_date": "2026-07-13", "heading": "Regulation 66", "id": "17e19e3a-4b7f-5df7-91b8-852b5d386c13", "identifiers": {"legislation.gov.uk:number": "249", "legislation.gov.uk:provision": "66", "legislation.gov.uk:type": "ssi", "legislation.gov.uk:year": "2021"}, "jurisdiction": "uk", "kind": "regulation", "language": "en", "legal_identifier": "SSI 2021/249 reg. 66", "level": 1, "metadata": {"extent": ["S"], "references_to": ["ssi/2021/249"], "retrieved_at": null}, "ordinal": 66, "source_as_of": "2026-07-13", "source_document_id": "ssi/2021/249", "source_format": "legislation.gov.uk-clml", "source_id": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/regulation/66", "source_path": "sources/uk/regulation/2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital-r2026-07-20-datefix/ssi/2021/249/regulation-66.xml", "source_url": "http://www.legislation.gov.uk/ssi/2021/249/regulation/66", "version": "2026-07-13-uk-ctr-sc-income-capital-r2026-07-20-datefix"}
